wb-mqtt-zigbee (1.3.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Rename package wb-zigbee2mqtt -> wb-mqtt-zigbee, Python package wb.mqtt_zigbee
  * Use friendly_name as WB device_id, auto-remove old package
  * Add command debounce with optimistic update to prevent value flickering
  * Add device_type, last_seen controls, range sliders, ghost/stale cleanup
  * Validate MQTT topics, handle callback errors, restore commands on reconnect

 -- Victor Fedorov <victor.fedorov@wirenboard.com>  Mon, 24 Mar 2026 14:00:00 +0300

wb-zigbee2mqtt (1.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add device discovery and real-time state updates from z2m exposes
  * Add expose type mapping: numeric (10 types), binary, enum, text, composite, rgb
  * Add RGB color picker for color lights (HS→RGB via colorsys)
  * Add device removal and rename handling
  * Add MQTT reconnect with full resubscription and device republish
  * Use ieee_address as stable WB device_id

